{
  "stem": "2690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 29.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know the date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I gave a date and I gave a place in England and she took it all down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, had the war taken longer, I would have been thrown out of that place, [LAUGHS] all of us, you know, because nothing was true what I said.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had to say something to get her off my husband's back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So now you were together in Vittel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Vittel, we were together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end of 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband and my daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also in Vittel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- my one brother was living in England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in-- he was a RAF, with the RAF.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was living in England.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my other brother, as a Britisher, was sent to a place in Poland in a camp, but it was not in a-- a-- a-- it was an internment camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because one of the Nazis said to him, I'll exchange places with you anytime because [INTERPOSING VOICES].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, that was very important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all, except one sister was born in Holland, and that's why she was sent to Bergen-Belsen with her husband.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because she had a passport with her, a Dutch passport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- we never said that my husband was her brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never said that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we-- we kept everything on the QT.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In France, we were liberated in '44 because Paris was liberated earlier than Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went from one camp to another camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Americans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember them very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the nicest people I had ever met, the nicest soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were so kind to us, and especially to my daughter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there was one soldier who said, I have a little girl like that, and I miss her lots, that I'm not with her.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
